<conjf>Starched</conjf> <pr>(st⟦aum⟧rcht)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Starching</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To stiffen with
starch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

